and I said, "Why?"

00:02:30.441 --> 00:02:32.158
And she said,

00:02:32.182 --> 00:02:35.821
"I was looking at pictures
of what life is like in Syria,

00:02:35.845 --> 00:02:39.355
and I thought I was going to go
and live in the Islamic Disney World."

00:02:40.527 --> 00:02:42.611
That's what she saw in ISIS.

00:02:42.635 --> 00:02:46.127
